Location, location, location! Conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, and the interstate. You will love the cozy feel of the hardwood floors, the updates of roof, kitchen, and bath, and the conveniences like the two car garage! Entertain your friends and family in the living room or take the party outside to  the patio. Move right in to 
this lovingly cared for home.  You will be happy to call it yours!
